The 9 Domains

The Shape of Human Health, Wealth & Wellness.

The 9 Domains & 56 Processes of the Humaucracy Care System. Humaucracy recognizes the variety of influences on your health. We thus help you optimize your Health by addressing 9 areas.


Click & Interact with the domains below to find out more information!

Cognition • Mindfulness

When was the last time your doctor listened to you talk about your ideas about your health? Humaucracy is committed to working with you to optimize your health. Being mindful of you in every aspect is something your Humaucracy Provider is trained to do.

Whats On Your Mind?

Sex • Compassion

Have you ever felt uncomfortable talking about your sexual, reproductive, or GI health? You can count on Humaucracy Provider to treat your concerns in the most professional manner. Humaucracy believes that, like Emotion, Sexual health is a very important yet often overlooked influence on people's health.

Do You Use Oral Contraceptives?

Health • Discipline

Does your current health care provider intervene only when you're sick, leaving you with a bill & no health promotion? Humaucracy will be there through sickness and in health: we're your Provider when you're sick and your coach you when you're well. We believe building on your healthy habits when your are well will build a healthier you.

Are You Feeling Well?

Money • Wisdom

Has money ever stressed you out? It's a well-known fact that stress induces illness, and one of the #1 stressors of people & communities is money. Humaucracy is one of the few health care organizations that brings your financial health and physical health together as one, helping you optimize your health & wealth in unison.

How Are Your Finances?

You • Individual

A fully stocked kitchen with all modern amenities provides a peaceful cooking environment.

What Makes You Tick?

Diet • Energy

It's well known that your diet can direct your health. But when was the last time your health care provider not only told you what to eat, but also provided the coaching & tools to succeed? Your Humaucracy Provider will develop a more personal relationship with you as you improve your eating habits, striving with you to achieve your dietary health goals.

What Are You Eating?

Stress / Illness • Entropy

Everyone gets sick sometime and when you do it's nice to know that Humaucracy's trained, licensed Providers are there to care for you. Right in your home if you like! No need to drag yourself to a clinic or hospital full of other sick people to share more germs with. Our licensed Providers can administer most common treatments right at home. We're happy to stop by, as we are out in your community already!

Who Is Managing Your Diabetes?

Community • Generosity

Do you feel your community can effect your health? Does your health care organization actively improve the health of your community? Humaucracy takes the stance that healthy communities produce healthy people, & therefore works to enhance the health, wealth, & well-being of both. Look for us- in our unique purple scrub uniforms- getting involved in your community!

How's The Neighborhood?

Emotion • Patience

Do you feel like your health care provider cares about your emotional health? Humaucracy - pulling from a large pool of Health Care evidence- believes your emotional health underlies many other facets of your health, yet it is often overlooked. You can thus trust your Humaucracy Provider to be patient & professional should you care to share your emotional health concerns.

How Are You Feeling?
